'''硫酸铁铵'''（化学式：NH<sub>4</sub>Fe(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>·12H<sub>2</sub>O或NH<sub>4</sub>[Fe(H<sub>2</sub>O)<sub>6</sub>](SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>·6 H<sub>2</sub>O），也被称为铁明矾。是一種[[复盐|复盐]]，属于[[矾|矾]]类。<ref>Considine, Douglas M: ''Chemical and process technology encyclopedia'', McGraw-Hill, New York, 1974, p. 993</ref>它看起来是淡紫色的八面体[[晶体|晶体]]。关于晶体颜色的来源已有一些讨论，有人将其归因于化合物中的杂质<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Christensen | first1 = Odin T | title = On the Cause of the Amethyst Color of Ferric Alum and of Mixed Crystals of Ferric and Manganic Alum | journal = Chem. Lab. Roy. Vet. Agr. Hochschule, KGL. Danske Vidsk. Selsk. Forh. | volume = 1906 | pages = 173–95 }}</ref>，也有人则声称是晶体本身的特性。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Bonnell | first1 = Jane | last2 = Philip Perman | first2 = Edgar | year = 1921 | title = CCXXIX.—The colour of iron alum | url = https://zenodo.org/record/1609699 | journal = J. Chem. Soc., Trans. | volume = 119 | pages = 1994–1997 | doi = 10.1039/CT9211901994 | access-date = 2022-01-15 | archive-date = 2022-01-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220115004221/https://zenodo.org/record/1609699 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

硫酸铁铵有[[顺磁性|顺磁性]]和[[酸性|酸性]]，且对[[微生物|微生物]]有毒性。它是一种弱氧化剂，能被还原为[[莫尔盐|莫尔盐]]。

==制备==
硫酸铁铵可以通过从[[硫酸铁|硫酸铁]]和[[硫酸铵|硫酸铵]]溶液中结晶来制备。通过加入[[硫酸|硫酸]]和[[硝酸|硝酸]]，[[硫酸亚铁|硫酸亚铁]]中的亚铁离子被氧化成硫酸铁。向溶液中加入硫酸铵时，会产生硫酸铁铵晶体沉淀。以下方程式忽略了[[结晶水|结晶水]]。

'''氧化'''：6 FeSO<sub>4</sub> + 2 HNO<sub>3</sub> + 3 H<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub> = 3 Fe<sub>2</sub>(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub> + 2 NO + 4 H<sub>2</sub>O

'''化合'''：Fe<sub>2</sub>(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub> + (NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub> = 2 NH<sub>4</sub>Fe(SO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>

==用途==
硫酸铁铵可用于[[废水|废水]]处理<ref name="ReferenceA">''Wiley Encyclopedia of inorganic chemistry'': Volume 4, p. 1704:</ref>、皮革[[鞣制|鞣制]]<ref name="ReferenceA" />、[[染料|染料]]生产<ref name="ReferenceA" />以及作为[[电子元件|电子元件]]生产中的[[蚀刻|蚀刻]]剂<ref>Chen et al.: ''United States Patent 5518131'' – "Etching molydbenum with ferric sulfate and ferric ammonium sulfate"</ref>。它已被广泛应用于绝热[[制冷|制冷]]设备<ref>Grant W. Wilson, Peter T. Timbie: "Construction techniques for adiabatic demagnetization refrigerators using ferric ammonium alum". ''Cryogenics'', Volume 39, Number 4, (1999) , pp. 319–322</ref> 、生化[[分析化学|分析]]<ref>J. C. Whitehorn: "A system of blood analysis. Supplement II. Simplified method for the determination of chlorides in blood or plasma". ''Journal of Biological Chemistry'' (1921), 45 p. 449–60.</ref>和[[有机合成|有机合成]]<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Yu | first1 = Shanxin | display-authors = etal   | year = 2005 | title = Application of ammonium ferric sulfate dodecahydrate in organic synthesis | journal = General Review | volume = 17 | issue = 1| pages = 27–30 }}</ref>等。

